021 年令人驚嘆的電影。」安薩爾諾夫補充。<br />\n<br />\n此舉一定會對 HBO Max 帶來大量的全新用戶，對於一個剛剛上線的串流平台來說是一個非常好的成長機會，但是同時也必須承擔無法在北美獲得票房收益的損失，但全年度的電影都採用此辦法，絕對也會增加使用者的黏著度，因此其主要競爭對手 Disney+、APPLE TV+ 甚至是領導品牌 NETFLIX 會以什麼樣的方式應對、跟進，相當令人好奇。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:50:41.000Z","msg":"HBO有冇4K HDR?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T05:10:06.000Z","msg":"Wonder Woman 1984 will be the first title that HBO Max streams in 4K<br />\nWith full support for Dolby Vision and Atmos<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2020/12/1/21813364/wonder-woman-1984-4k-ultra-hd-dolby-vision-atmos-announced\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2020%2F12%2F1%2F21813364%2Fwonder-woman-1984-4k-ultra-hd-dolby-vision-atmos-announced&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGNqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=10561c6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2020/12/1/21813364/wonder-woman-1984-4k-ultra-hd-dolby-vision-atmos-announced</a>"},{"pid":"d620305833b9bf2802c2c883ddeaa6ef7bf98150","tid":2311131,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T05:11:04.000Z","msg":"爆谷片係屋企睇冇咁好睇"},{"pid":"e5e81e0a177a74fc8c351b553bab13e6caefd80f","tid":2311131,"uid":96788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4110bf4226b34d5e28ff154fe019eff49c7c2cf3","tid":2311131,"uid":11676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ab2d813c1a268987506150ee07d554ad53e85ff","tid":2311131,"uid":64922,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c4d4991440b4e71a89f88c4c6c72ed8fe8ce8bc","tid":2311131,"uid":84018,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:21:07.000Z","msg":"咁香港 睇唔睇到 HBO Go/ Now E"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:01:33.000Z","msg":"因華納依個步署<br />\n老美本土hbomax<br />\n將會cut左7日免費試睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T03:31:17.000Z","msg":"香港人麻煩繼續去戲院睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/do